Students can be assigned to groups in several ways:


by pressing the Group button in the Whole group tab ( ) you can quickly assign all the students in the class to one group;

right click on a student icon and assign a group from the drop down menu;

select several students in the class, then right click, and assign selected students to a group from the drop down menu;

select one or more students, then select the Group tab and click on a group (see  ).

